<h2><a id="changes" name="changes">Changes from Previous Version</a></h2>

<p>In <a href="#summary">3.5. Summary</a>, changed 'text/html' for
HTML 4 as <strong>SHOULD</strong> rather than <strong>MAY</strong>.</p>

<p>Updated <a href="#ref-xhtml1">reference to XHTML 1.0</a> to refer
to the Second Edition.</p>

